\F[nakosu_angry]Nadeshiko: "As I thought... you were lying in wait...
Akane."

\FF[furi_smile]Akane: "You knew and yet you came here... That takes
courage. You're serious, aren't you, Nadeshiko?♪"

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "I'm always serious. I haven't lied to you even
once, Akane!"

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[2]Akane: "Even if I try to persuade you, you won't listen...
not the Nadeshiko of now."

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Of course. Because... the Akane of now isn't the
real Akane."

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[furi_smile]\AA[2]Akane: "Then... maybe I should have everyone convince you♪
Stubborn Nadeshiko might respond better to that approach♪"

\FF[yuri_free]Yurika: "Nadeshiko... no, White Tiger. We were wrong. We
didn't realize the wonderfulness of becoming free like this.
This freedom is a reward from our master♪"

\FF[yuri_free]Yurika: "It's irresistible♪ I want to teach you this
happiness too♪ To become one with our master. You want to
become one with our master too, don't you, Nadeshiko?"
\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[yuri_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "President... I..."

\FF[iruka_free]Iruka: "You should just say you want to if that's how you
really feel♪ White Tiger, you're always so tsundere. It'd be
easier if you just admitted it♪"

\FF[inu_free]Anna Maple: "Because my education hasn't been thorough
enough, we're causing trouble for our master～♪ My class only
allows free students! Stiff White Tiger, you better reform
quickly♪"
\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[inu_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Senpai... Teacher..."

\FF[ajiri_free]Sora: "They say people are born with roles to play, but
that's a bunch of lies♪ If you're dyed in one single
feeling, nothing is difficult. Just live freely, that's all
there is to it♪"
\FF[sumire_free]
\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[sumire_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "That's not what freedom is!"

\FF[himawari_free]
\FF[syuu_free]

\F[nakosu_angry]\FF[himawari_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "That's because everyone has turned into
monsters...!"
\FF[ayaka_free]
\FF[ayaka_free]
\FF[ayaka_free]
\F[nakosu_trouble]\FF[ayaka_free]\AA[1]Nadeshiko: "Hate Akane...? There's no way..."

\F[nakosu_trouble]Nadeshiko: "Enough... enough already! I want to talk just
with you! Akane!!"

\FF[furi_smile]Akane: "Make sure to listen to what everyone has to say,
Nadeshiko."
